                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6585" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10072 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蜜雪冰城：“雪王”的出圈之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MXBC: The way out of the circle of &quot;Snow King&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于树江，刘书敏，李艳双</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蜜雪冰城股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蜜雪冰城；品牌定位；品牌营销；钻石模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MXBC; Brand positioning; Brand marketing; Diamond model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奶茶作为一种休闲消费饮品，兼备口感与颜值两方面优点，深受年轻一代消费者的追捧。茶饮行业毛利高且周转快，对商家来说是巨大的市场，因此竞争激烈。奶茶行业虽也受到疫情影响，但头部品牌的业绩整体增长速度仍然不低，优势突出。而有一家平价的奶茶店在各类竞争者中“杀出重围”，其在国内拥有超过10000家门店，位居国内茶饮品牌首位，企业估值达到200亿元。近日更是通过主题曲等各种话题，在互联网各大平台撬动了千万流量。
本案例以这家起源于河南省的奶茶品牌——蜜雪冰城为研究对象，重点介绍其创始人的创业经历，品牌从做好产品、锁定目标顾客、建立供应链降低成本到目前“雪王”IP诞生并在微博、抖音等各大平台引起关注的一系列过程。案例旨在分析蜜雪冰城品牌营销采取的策略，在愈加激烈的市场竞争背景下为各类茶饮品牌提供适当的借鉴和参考。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leisure consumption drink, milk tea has the advantages of both taste and appearance, and is popular among the younger generation of consumers. The tea industry has high gross profit and fast turnover, which is a huge market for merchants, so the competition is fierce. Although the milk tea industry has also been affected by the epidemic, the overall growth rate of the performance of the head brand is still not low and its advantages are prominent. One affordable milk tea shop &quot;broke through the encirclement&quot; among various competitors. It has more than 10000 stores in China, ranking first among the domestic tea brands, and the enterprise value reached 20 billion yuan. Recently, through various topics such as theme songs, tens of millions of traffic have been leveraged on major platforms of the Internet.
This case takes the milk tea brand - MXBC, which originated in Henan Province, as the research object, and focuses on the entrepreneurial experience of its founder. The brand has gone through a series of processes from making good products, locking target customers, establishing a supply chain and reducing costs to the birth of &quot;Snow King&quot; IP and attracting attention on Weibo, Tiktok and other platforms. The purpose of the case is to analyze the strategies adopted by the brand marketing of MXBC, and provide appropriate reference for various tea brands under the increasingly fierce market competition.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">细分市场；品牌定位钻石模型；品牌营销；国产品牌迅速崛起的时代背景；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
